[inference]
template_type: KnowAct
lexicon_terms:
- emit
- track
- observe
contract:
  input:
    diagnostic_output: object
    convergence_metric: number
  output:
    cns_span: object
    emission_status: string
energy_cap: 1024
visibility: Public
---
{# Template: gentle-lovelace/gentle-cns-emit.j2 #}
{# goal: Deterministically emit CNS span with per-dimension writing quality scores and convergence state for variety tracking. #}

[inference]
temperature = 0.1
reasoning_effort = "low"
verbosity = "terse"
max_tokens = 256
thinking_budget = "off"

{% set scores = diagnostic_output.dimension_scores | default({}) %}
{% set recs = diagnostic_output.recommendations | default([]) %}

Emit a CNS span for gentle-lovelace variety tracking. Return the observation deterministically from the provided diagnostic output.

Input:
```json
{
  "diagnostic_output": {{ diagnostic_output | tojson }},
  "convergence_metric": {{ convergence_metric }}
}
```

Return JSON only — use the actual values from diagnostic_output, do not fabricate:
```json
{
  "cns_span": {
    "namespace": "cns.gentle_lovelace",
    "observation": {
      "dimension_scores": {
        "accessibility": {{ scores.accessibility | default(0.0) }},
        "precision": {{ scores.precision | default(0.0) }},
        "findability": {{ scores.findability | default(0.0) }},
        "agent_correctness": {{ scores.agent_correctness | default(0.0) }}
      },
      "overall_score": {{ diagnostic_output.overall_score | default(0.0) }},
      "convergence_metric": {{ convergence_metric }},
      "recommendation_count": {{ recs | length }}
    }
  },
  "emission_status": "emitted"
}
```
